    <p>Et odio pellentesque diam volutpat commodo sed. Tortor at risus viverra
        adipiscing at in. Ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. psum dolor sit amet,
        consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et
        dolore magna aliqua!</p>
    <p><em>Comment By: <strong>Cody Python</strong> on Sunday, October 9th, 2022</em></p>
</div>
<div class="dropdown">
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary dropdown-toggle" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false"
        data-bs-auto-close="outside">Leave Comment</button>
    <form class="dropdown-menu p-4">

        <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="DropdownFormComment" class="form-label d-flex justify-content-start">Comment</label>

            <textarea name="comment" id="DropdownFormComment" cols="100" rows="10"
                placeholder="write comment here"></textarea>
            <br>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary d-flex justify-content-end">Post Comment</button>
        </div>
    </form>
    <button class="btn btn-outline-success update" type="submit">
        Update Post
    </button>
    <button class="btn btn-outline-success delete" type="submit">
        Delete Post
    </button>
</div>